  "title": "Assistant Restaurant Manager (up to $4,500 base | Italian Restaurant)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Assist in supervising and coordinating front-of-house operations.</li><li>Ensure service quality, cleanliness, and compliance with hygiene standards.</li><li>Support recruitment, onboarding, and training of new team members.</li><li>Monitor staff attendance, scheduling, and performance.</li><li>Handle guest enquiries, feedback, and complaints promptly.</li><li>Oversee stock levels and liaise with suppliers for replenishment.</li><li>Support reporting, cash handling, and administrative tasks.</li><li>Take charge of operations in the absence of the Restaurant Manager.</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>Minimum <strong>2 years</strong> of experience in a supervisory role within F&B or hospitality.</li><li>Strong customer service and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Proactive team player with good communication and leadership qualities.</li><li>Familiar with POS systems and daily cash handling procedures.</li><li>Diploma or Certificate in Hospitality or related field is an advantage.</li><li>Willing to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays.</li></ul><p>Tyson Jay Management Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 24C2479</p><p>Ivan Lim | EA Personnel No.: R1109856</p>",
